headline: Is Duke Energy (DUK) Priced Fairly After Its Strong Multi Year Share Price Run?
summary: If you are wondering whether Duke Energy's current share price truly reflects its value, you are not alone. This article is built to help you size that up with a clear valuation lens. Duke Energy's stock recently closed at US$128.20, with returns of 5.2% over 7 days, 7.5% over 30 days, 9.2% year to date, 18.9% over 1 year, 44.8% over 3 years and 76.0% over 5 years. headline: Trump trade adviser Navarro says administration may force data center builders like Meta to 'internalize' costs
summary: Data centers powering artificial intelligence have strained the electrical grid and driven utility costs higher for consumers.
